ssets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係屌佢老母嬲撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多零碎例子數唔哂, 例如無啦啦會好似隻狗咁咬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明有時玩下係無問題, 但有時講咗話再咬痛都仲唔收手, 到我嬲果陣又嬲我做乜嬲佢, 我屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n唉.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔打啦, 再打落去 1001都有, 都係至在上黎呻兩句  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195ec0121e83394eeac46ecbc20c558e71520947","tid":916933,"uid":112390,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"快d分<br />\n呢d女人娶唔過<br />\n更加唔會分擔你啲壓力"},{"pid":"b1d74ceea7095e359964aa9e11de649fd47c2f9b","tid":916933,"uid":140604,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"擺我上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分手啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05210a52ac00958b2b6be17a408e635739cd641c","tid":916933,"uid":140363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"以前條女都咁上下<br />\n 係副計正好砌先keep 得耐"},{"pid":"f08252ef82067ea06ba6bf0d91b87c2ba6a7d7fb","tid":916933,"uid":203526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1d74ceea7095e359964aa9e11de649fd47c2f9b","tid":916933,"uid":140604,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"擺我上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分手啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"笑咗一笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx for sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bebf877b9d7ca5f4048bdb2b9c0c9ad91a2a0f3","tid":916933,